data.description: So many possibilities!!!!  Enjoy living on this nearly 1.5 acre property.  This spacious house offers a variety of amenities that are sure to meet your needs. Inside, you'll find 4 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, providing ample space for everyone in the household.  A sun porch, where you can relax and enjoy your morning coffee, large dining and living rooms. The back patio provides a perfect space for outdoor entertaining or simply unwinding after a long day. For those with a green thumb, a greenhouse is included, allowing you to indulge in your love for gardening. With a large garage, and connecting utility sheds you'll have plenty of space for parking, projects and storage.The full basement offers additional storage or can be transformed into a recreational area. Situated on a large property, you'll have plenty of room to roam and enjoy the outdoors.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home.  Professional pictures to come. This is a multi use porperty zoned residential and commercial. Reach out today for more infomation.
